\forall{n}\in{N}:1(1!)+2(2!)+3(3!)+...+n(n!)=(n+1)!-1
1(1!)=(1+1)!-1
1=1
\forall{k}\in{N}:1(1!)+2(2!)+3(3!)+...+k(k!)=(k+1)!-1
1(1!)+2(2!)+3(3!)+...+k(k!)=(k+1)!-1
1(1!)+2(2!)+3(3!)+...+k(k!)+(k+1)(k+1)!=(k+1)!-1+(k+1)(k+1)!
1(1!)+2(2!)+3(3!)+...+k(k!)+(k+1)(k+1)!=(k+1)!(k+2)-1)
(k + 1)! \cdot (k+2) - 1 = (k + 2)! - 1
(k+1)! \cdot (k+1) - 1
